  <WestTek_OpportunitySite_AncientWestTekLaboratory.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.2>DiscoveryDesc(discovered==true)-&gt;場所を特定しました</WestTek_OpportunitySite_AncientWestTekLaboratory.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.2>
